               <msContents>
                  <summary/>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i0">
                     <locus from="1v" to="13v">1v-13v</locus>
                     <textLang xml:lang="ar">Arabic</textLang>
                     <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT0049IHA#s24IHA">قران, Seventeenth ǧuz’ (17/30)</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#1v">-1v</locus>سورة الأنبيإ عليهم السّلام مأية واثني عشر اية مكية \ بِسْم اللهِ الرَّحْمَنِ الرَّحِيْمِ , إِقْتَرَبَ لِلْنَّاسِ حِسَابُهُمْ وَهُمْ فِيْ غَفْلَةٍ مُّعْرِضُوْنَ</incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#13v">-13v</locus>وَأَتُوْا الزَّكَوْةَ وَاُعْتَصِمُوْا بِاللهِ هُوَ مَولَاكُمْ فَنِعْمَ المَوْلَيْ ونِعْمَ الـنَّصِيْرُ</explicit>
                     <note>21:1-22:78. Title of suras rubricated in red. Three commas in red as verse markers. Words : "لا اله الا" and "لا اله الا انت" rubricated in black and red color (2v, 6r). Twelve lines to a page. Few words completed on the following line. Vowels with a thinner qalam. Corrections (10r, 11r). In the margins, mark of ǧuz’ in red color (1v), mark of ḥizb (7v), mark of saǧda (9r), all with elaborations.</note>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
